<p>We use a modified version of the <%= link_to "textile", "http://redcloth.org/textile", :target => "_blank" %> markup language
which allows you to add some formatting to your description.</p>

<p>The following tags (and [attributes]) are supported:</p>

<table class="table table-bordered table-condensed">
  <thead><th>Description</th><th>Example</th><th>Tag</th><th>Supported attributes</th><th>Comments</th></thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr><td>Strong importance</td><td>We will *never* let you down</td><td>strong</td><td></td><td>displayed as bold</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Stress emphasis</td><td>We are _very_ reliable</td><td>em</td><td></td><td>displayed as italic</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Link</td><td>Visit our "website":http://www.example.com</td><td>a</td><td>href title</td><td>nofollow is used, and links open in new tab</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Line break</td><td>Roses are red,<br />Violets are blue</td><td>br</td><td></td><td></td></tr>
